data.description: A charming 3 bed/2 bath single-family home in the mountains of Carnuel gracefully perched on nearly two acres of land. The interior is a symphony of comfort and sophistication with an inviting doorway, large windows, and wood stove. The kitchen is equipped with updated appliances. In this mountainous retreat, every day is like a serene getaway to create a truly enchanting home that perfectly captures the allure of living in the mountains while being close to the city. Aspects I love about the home is the unspoiled natural beauty surrounding the house, the privacy and space, the spectacular views, and the adventurous exploration around the house.
